channel.title: How do i make a dark bow or seercull shoot 2 arrows?
channel.description: any1 know how i can make a darkbow like rs or seercull shoot 2 arrows? and give it a spec that shoots 4 arrows but uses all the spec bar? can any1 help me out ?

item.title: How do i make a dark bow or seercull shoot 2 arrows?
item.dc:creator: @Inmate1 Inmate™
item.description:
@Inmate1 wrote:

exe626:

Erm, I believe the term is ‘style delay’ but I don’t remember. Attack every 100ms[every 1.5 seconds] Then press the special bar and do it 2 times? I ain’t too firmular with the coding, but you need a new int that controls the delays in sections like that, and then you need to set the right I.D. to shoot double when the special bar interface is selected. Does moparscape even have darkbows now?

Sorry mate to dissapoint you. We make double projectiles + double hits… The 2nd projectile finished -1 the first.
Then we use a hitDelay to hit 2times.
